action.text:
A powerful reality check from @edmylett that everyone scrolling needs to hear right now. The highlight reel isn't the full story, and what shows up in your feed is carefully curated – not the complete truth. He's cutting through the noise to remind us that comparison is the thief of joy, especially when you're comparing your real life to someone else's filtered version.
